<h2 id="orgc5169c5">Some final remarks</h2>
<ul>
<li class="fragment roll-in">These are not to be construed as definitive</li>
<li class="fragment roll-in">Your mileage may vary!</li>
<li class="fragment roll-in">This is offered as a method to help <b>you</b> decide what CAS would best suit 
<b>your</b> course and <b>your</b> students</li>

<li class="fragment roll-in">Thank you all!</li>

</ul>
